1 0 0 1 50 800 Tm (˙Fikisha App Overview \(Simple Version\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 786 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 772 Tm (Fikisha is a hyperlocal delivery app.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 758 Tm (That means it connects people with nearby shops and delivers orders quickly within the same local area.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 744 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 730 Tm (What the app does) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 716 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 702 Tm (1. Customers order from nearby stores) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 688 Tm (- People open the app, choose products from local shops, and place orders.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 674 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm (2. Stores receive and prepare orders) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm (- Merchants see incoming orders, confirm them, and get them ready for pickup.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (3. Drivers deliver to customers) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm (- Drivers are assigned nearby deliveries and update status from pickup to drop-off.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm (4. Admins manage the whole system) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (- Admins oversee users, stores, drivers, payments, support, zones, and reports.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (How it works) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm (1. Different apps for different people) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm (- Customer app for buying) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm (- Merchant app for store operations) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm (- Driver workflow for deliveries) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm (- Admin dashboard for control and monitoring) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 422 Tm (2. One central backend) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 408 Tm (- All apps send requests to a central system that processes orders and updates everyone in real time.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 380 Tm (3. Location-based matching) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 366 Tm (- Orders are matched to nearby stores and drivers to keep delivery fast and local.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 352 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 338 Tm (4. Secure access by role) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 324 Tm (- Each user only sees what they are allowed to use \(customer, merchant, driver, admin\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 310 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 296 Tm (5. Tracking and business control) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm (- The platform tracks orders, payments, and operational activity with logs and reports.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 268 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 254 Tm (One-line summary) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 240 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 226 Tm (Fikisha is a local commerce and delivery platform that helps customers buy from nearby businesses, merchants sell efficiently, drivers earn through deliveries, and admins run everything securely.) Tj
